title: Excel Agents - MediationZone Documentation 9.3 - InfoZone
text: This section describes the Excel Decoder and Excel Encoder agents which are processing agents for batch workflow configurations. These agents convert Excel files into UDRs to be routed into a workflow, and then converts the UDRs back into an Excel file to be delivered to the output destination. Open The section contains the following subsections: Excel Decoder Agent Excel Encoder Agent Excel Agents UDR Types
